The paper deals with entropy concentration, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). It also involves sequences and constraints, which are common in data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG). The maximum entropy method is often used in computational complexity (cs.CC) and statistical inference (cs.SI). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely to contain this paper.
